# This file doesn't set colorsets because they're set externally

AddToDecor "plain"  BorderStyle Simple
AddToDecor "plain"  TitleStyle Centered
AddToDecor "plain"  TitleStyle Height 24

+ ButtonStyle Reset
+ ButtonStyle All -- UseTitleStyle
+ ButtonStyle 4 Vector 5 \
        25x75@0 45x75@0 45x55@0 25x55@1 25x75@1
+ ButtonStyle 3 Vector 17 \
        20x20@1 30x20@1 50x40@1 70x20@1 \
        80x20@1 80x30@0 60x50@0 80x70@1 \
        80x80@0 70x80@0 50x60@0 30x80@0 \
        20x80@0 20x70@0 40x50@1 20x30@0 20x20@1

IconFont -adobe-helvetica-medium-r-normal--10-100-75-75-p-56-iso8859-1
*FvwmIconMan: 1 Font -adobe-helvetica-medium-r-normal--10-100-75-75-p-56-iso8859-1

MenuStyle * MenuColorset 0
MenuStyle * BorderWidth 2
MenuStyle * TrianglesRelief
MenuStyle * Font -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-normal--12-120-75-75-p-70-iso8859-1
MenuStyle * SidePic

Style * Colorset 0
Style * HilightColorset 1
Style * BorderWidth  4
Style * HandleWidth  6
Style * Font -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-normal--14-140-75-75-p-82-iso8859-1
Style * MwmBorder
Style * MwmButtons

Style * UseDecor plain

*FvwmPager: Colorset * 0
*FvwmPager: HilightColorset * 1
